The defendant Mory Anton Moore was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • Manufacture/Deliver Cocaine (>1-5g), a class F felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1)(cm)1r.
  • Maintain Drug Trafficking Place, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.42(1).

Defendant waives right to presentence investigation. Court orders on Count 1 - 2 years Wisconsin State Prison and 4 years Extended Supervision, concurrent with 21CF670; Count 2 - 1 1/2 years Wisconsin State Prison and 2 years Extended Supervision, concurrent with Count 1, any treatment deemed necessary, absolute sobriety, no alcohol or controlled substances unless prescribed by a medical provider, DOC collect costs, 134 days sentence credit.  Defendant is eligible for Challenge and Substance Abuse programs.
